搜索地址经常换，觉得搜索不能用了就用这源到浏览器搜索一下，把搜索出来的网址替换到搜索页面上最上面的网址比如
搜索出来网址https://g58xsf.56bok.com/modules/article/csykI1VmraB0Lex.php
原搜索地址https://g58xsf.56bok.com/modules/article/KcdrS0bX13orSr.php,{
  "charset": "gbk",
  "method": "POST",
  "body": "searchkey={{key}}&searchtype=all"
}
替换后
https://g58xsf.56bok.com/modules/article/csykI1VmraB0Lex.php,{
  "charset": "gbk",
  "method": "POST",
  "body": "searchkey={{key}}&searchtype=all"
